<concept id="concept_B32294CC9FA643A2A14A74B1DAA49C95" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Managing Organizations and Users</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>This chapter describes how to: </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Create an organization.</li>
                <li>Maintain the address data of organizations.</li>
                <li>Add a role to an organization.</li>
                <li>Manage user accounts: lock and unlock user accounts, and reset the password for a user.</li>
                <li>Register multiple users for organizations.</li>
                <li>Create and manage tenants connecting to OIDC providers.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
